    {
      "id": "PopularPost361018",
      "post_content": "Ugh, I wish they would have made this a one-drop.  \n  \nIt would have been a blue [Tormented Soul](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Tormented Soul) with the upside of also being a chump blocker and having some decent secondary use in lategame, but at the downside of being an easier target for removal.  \n  \nAs a two-drop, the Bestow cost is just frustratingly high.  \nWhy couldn't they make more than just the rare Bestow creatures constructed-viable?  \nOf course this would have made them powerful in limited - but not game-breaking.",
      "posted_by": "Mode",
